b'MD Student Services and Support'
b'caherman'
b'Academic Skills Services'
b'The director of academic skills in the Office of Student Affairs\xc2\xa0at the University of Illinois College of Medicine Rockford is focused on ensuring the academic success of all UICOMR students.'
b'The office is dedicated to serving a diverse population of students through a variety of services including:'
b'Learning Strategies'
b'The\xc2\xa0director of academic services supports all students who are looking for strategies in time management, organization, test-taking skills, and/or anything related to academic success.'
b'Students can set up an appointment to receive assistance in creating a study plan, discuss their learning and test-taking strategies, or figure out how to manage different tasks to reduce stress.'
b'Our Road to Residency Program\xc2\xa0also offers presentations on different learning strategies and tips for academic success in medical school.'
b'Road to Residency Program'
b'Additional Resources for Learning Strategies '
b'Additional Resources for Learning Strategies '
b'United States Medical Licensing Examination (USMLE) Preparation'
b'Academic Support provides numerous resources to assist students in the preparation of Step 1 and both components of Step 2, Clinical Knowledge (CK) and Clinical Skills (CS).\xc2\xa0 Students are required to pass Step 1 and both components of Step 2 prior to graduation.'
b'Step preparation resources are shared through Road to Residency presentations, individual appointments, and small group meetings. Please contact Director of Academic Services Stephanie Williams at smwilli7@uic.edu for more information.'
b'smwilli7@uic.edu'
b'Additional Resources:'
b'Test taking strategies'
b'Test taking strategies'
b'Step 1 Resources'
b'USMLE Bulletin'
b'USMLE Bulletin'
b'NBME'
b'NBME'
b'Peer Educators'
b'The Office of Student Affairs, in collaboration with the Office of Medical Education, offers an exceptional Peer Educator Program to assist students with review and application of course content. Please contact Director of Academic Services Stephanie Williams at\xc2\xa0smwilli7@uic.edu\xc2\xa0for more information.'
b'smwilli7@uic.edu'
